{"id": "1192287973589401760", "channel_id": "1192287973589401760", "type": 0, "author_id": "1119678312130822275", "author_name": "pokai2228", "author_bot": false, "content": "其實我已經猜到鏡像「可能」會做調整或削弱\n\n心眼利刃70+800x3約等於2500啊帶爆傷命輪（巨齒之刃還有那個狂氣爆發給25%爆率的）爆一下2500x2.3=5750（2.3是50+20+60還沒算造物有沒有加爆傷或傷害還有密契的東西）啊易傷（商店的易傷能刻在艾瓦爾的0費保留上要輸出在打出）5750x1.5=8625（後面有影片能參考但我盾沒滿而且有一些造物）\n現在沒太多人用只是因為很要求艾瓦爾三啟你才能把鏡像放上去後更好打出來\n\n我是覺得商店刷出鏡像對我的隊伍提升太多，其它刻印沒有鏡像20分之1強（隨便抓的數值）而且要是刷出兩三個商店鏡像那boss就不用玩了，我是覺得鏡像要做調整，不然現在刷商店出來的穩定性太低了而且不好玩，⭐️我的想法是精英戰後可以放棄造物和錢去刻印一個鏡像，啊商店和普通戰鬥後就別出鏡像不然上限太高⭐️\n\n其實要是刪鏡像也還行反正我應該能買一些妙手或加抽牌的造物這樣能比較快再抽到心眼利刃\n我的隊伍目前長這樣\n（我喚醒體等級都50級我懶得打那些東西讓我升60）\n最後一隻能換（在等莉莉或神父）\n我不喜歡用拉蒙娜我覺得她的指令卡很不符合我的盾隊", "timestamp": "2024-01-04T02:06:44.543000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👏", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1192287975086772265", "filename": "IMG_4877.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1717546, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1192287973589401760/1192287975086772265/IMG_4877.png?ex=6a0090f4&is=69ff3f74&hm=7e7e0139ef82d03c745d16c1fcf7f9ad3637a5e39cc214a05724c192a3386c59&"}, {"id": "1192287975648788500", "filename": "IMG_4878.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1713410, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1192287973589401760/1192287975648788500/IMG_4878.png?ex=6a0090f5&is=69ff3f75&hm=699bc95a9feb2a4cf026f43c7d9c3230caa0a1b1017c7d81659a5011ee9589c8&"}, {"id": "1192287976185675797", "filename": "IMG_4879.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1640468, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1192287973589401760/1192287976185675797/IMG_4879.png?ex=6a0090f5&is=69ff3f75&hm=fdfae6372694c8570dafa1ab16d7db5866decbbde1c960b798b2759eb1fc7b44&"}, {"id": "1192287976709967929", "filename": "IMG_4880.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1706444, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1192287973589401760/1192287976709967929/IMG_4880.png?ex=6a0090f5&is=69ff3f75&hm=b9696b6ff8caf29e37805e87c0761986ae90984a69787e909cb4e7138ef0f7f1&"}, {"id": "1192287977292972084", "filename": "IMG_4881.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1711831, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1192287973589401760/1192287977292972084/IMG_4881.png?ex=6a0090f5&is=69ff3f75&hm=a47edfa30e2e5336e58b4b75b57ce2481dcc5bcac93769fd25ea6258ea81bf47&"}, {"id": "1192287977867595786", "filename": "IMG_4882.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1636775, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1192287973589401760/1192287977867595786/IMG_4882.png?ex=6a0090f5&is=69ff3f75&hm=8b54a5932f365ace8e70f5e93b9687a3d9f1ccf1f455d71c21bcc55ef830cd01&"}, {"id": "1192287978802905088", "filename": "IMG_4884.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1707348, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1192287973589401760/1192287978802905088/IMG_4884.png?ex=6a0090f5&is=69ff3f75&hm=9449c35a597d1f52df8019cbf418a82cc1cdca6861db9bbb36ac8b1e9eca7327&"}, {"id": "1192287979402706986", "filename": "IMG_4885.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1673306, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1192287973589401760/1192287979402706986/IMG_4885.png?ex=6a0090f5&is=69ff3f75&hm=34c7c34c0e1cb162fe1674ec783dec0a52e690a1ab41b734235755c1fdb0259c&"}, {"id": "1192287979847307354", "filename": "IMG_4886.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1643858, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1192287973589401760/1192287979847307354/IMG_4886.png?ex=6a0090f6&is=69ff3f76&hm=7ae8b561eec53a89ea856b17fd4247c9855b9b2e0966d94cd3a3bf98acec29ed&"}, {"id": "1192287980354797588", "filename": "RPReplay_Final1704169805.mov", "content_type": "video/quicktime", "size": 10413604, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1192287973589401760/1192287980354797588/RPReplay_Final1704169805.mov?ex=6a0090f6&is=69ff3f76&hm=47af290f517ad4fcf69323756004123f5b7228619476b2a01fdf9d4ecc87e748&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1192287973589401760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」我玩盾隊對鏡像的看法", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1192330115414229043", "channel_id": "1192330115414229043", "type": 0, "author_id": "371624648078524416", "author_name": "devis0212", "author_bot": false, "content": "如圖 就先不談數值了 \n在後期面對萬血boss沒有中毒命輪的珈倫\n那一點微薄的毒 微薄的補血還要有限制的虛弱\n到底有哪一點配得上他3費的價值\n寧菲亞裝上命輪 大約能有150左右的中毒量\n珈倫則只有50 誰會花高費去給boss上50中毒跟回20血 還要看算力夠不夠才有虛弱", "timestamp": "2024-01-04T04:54:11.937000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}, {"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1192330115854647306", "filename": "IMG_8241.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 332837, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1192330115414229043/1192330115854647306/IMG_8241.png?ex=6a00b834&is=69ff66b4&hm=277a56e2cd68fd0013a47b91c56490f7cdadfd85460846f9dff7dbd961b2444f&"}, {"id": "1192330116257284096", "filename": "IMG_8242.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 164243, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1192330115414229043/1192330116257284096/IMG_8242.png?ex=6a00b834&is=69ff66b4&hm=455c583ea4d13457ef86abb38f21bebc10d338c05e9e23de776231e98e1bbb1f&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1192330115414229043", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」珈倫技能存在意義", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1192397121085767760", "channel_id": "1192397121085767760", "type": 0, "author_id": "800269534521983028", "author_name": "lazydoge_", "author_bot": false, "content": "整个卡组就靠一张心眼利刃输出，不仅是复制卡牌，镜像刻印带来的保留也至关重要，要在手里捏着配合防御减费和大招叠盾打爆发，为了福袋删了镜像，那艾尔瓦也没法玩了啊", "timestamp": "2024-01-04T09:20:27.334000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1192397121085767760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」镜像刻印删除了艾尔瓦盾击流咋玩", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1192329124522491905", "channel_id": "1192329124522491905", "type": 0, "author_id": "456226577798135808", "author_name": "Deleted User", "author_bot": false, "content": "該討論串記錄忘卻炎上事件（會持續更新到本人退遊［短時間不會退遊］）\n事件記錄v1.3：\n1、同人比赛一等獎作文1000銀芯、畫畫2000銀芯，然後有玩家不滿，從而退遊，官方直接將作文1000銀芯改為2000銀芯（該事件，官方滑跪）\n2、UP池到手角色要削弱，補償方案搖擺而低廉\n3、為了削弱夫人隊伍要刪除鏡像刻印和複製卡牌事件，然後玩家抗議（所以目前官方說不刪除）\n4、開服才一個月，就要無光輪轉改成鎖角色鎖命輪（角色跟命輪都只能用一次）的狀態，然後24個角色跟48個命輪要輪流使用（目前版本未有這個舉動）\n5、pvp很多問題沒解決（觸手傷害機制；死亡與復活的機制；死亡角色將被清空狂氣條等等可以從本質上限制復活的系統；單人角色可以抽出重複的指示卡；pvp與獎勵互補，導致玩家生氣，因為這是強迫玩家玩pvp；pvp的部分角色過於強勢；pvp的數值設計的不均衡；段位太長）\n6、公會戰（使玩家強制社交）\n補充：\n1、官方如果滑跪，會在該事件後面補充說明\n2、如有問題，請跟我說，我馬上修改", "timestamp": "2024-01-04T04:50:15.690000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-06T15:33:31.603000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 16}, {"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 9}, {"emoji": "😅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1192329124522491905", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "炎上事件記錄區", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
